* Make a general list of staples needed such as flour, pancake mix,
cereal, canned items, pasta, sauce, cleaning and toiletry items.
* Call (973) 908-5985 on Monday or Thursday between 9am-5pm. You will be directed to call the volunteer assigned to that day. Simply provide us with the number you are feeding in your household.
* Arrange a specific time with your volunteer to have your request ready for pick up.
* The items will be waiting in bins outside the church kitchen doors.
